------

This is a Black Highlighter-based theme by [[*user GreenGolem]]. This was created as an alternative for the [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/theme:spc Sigma-9-based SPC theme]. This theme is created specifically for the Shark Punching Center GOI.

You need to import the Black Highlighter theme as well in order to use this theme. To learn more about the Black Highlighter theme, go [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/theme:black-highlighter-theme here].

**To import this theme, add this to your page:**
[[div class="code"]]
@@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:black-highlighter-theme]]@@
@@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:shark-punching-centre-bhl]]@@
[[/div]]

Horizontal rules are created with 5 hyphens "- - - - -" and extends across the entire page if not placed inside anything (eg a blockquote). The line separating pages of this document are horizontal rules.[[footnote]] This is a footnote. [[/footnote]]

Titles can be created by putting between 1 and 6 plus signs ("+") at the start of the line.

